187
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,230
It's fine. It's fine.

188
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:48,700
Each generation has their own predicament to deal with.

189
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,200
This one predicament

190
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:53,560
