191
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:57,150
Let me play against this old guy.

192
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,610
Greetings, Grandmaster.

193
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:04,080
Forego the formality.

194
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,870
I once told you

195
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,550
