215
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,270
There's no doubt that you'd go with them

216
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:59,550
to look for the last cold weapon.

217
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:00,960
For this reason,

218
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,790
